title: HAS SOMETHING CHANGED IN RANKED?
body: Im finding the games are way too easy. Its like bots have replaced players in ranked or somethings changed with the mmr?

replies.body: boosted players play on their accounts. which is more than half this garbage server.
Pre-season. No one is playing seriously.
Im on a 12 game winning streak. Its never happened before. My win rate is at 77%.
